title: Whats On Your Bucket List
itunes:title: Whats On Your Bucket List
description:
The Breakfast Club had Daryl Fairweather  stop by, to speak on rent spikes, black homeownership, redefining real estate and more. Afterwards Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a woman with an odd goal on her bucket list, which led them to open the phone lines to see what our listeners may have on their bucket list. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
